                            <comment id="13804171" author="brentworden" created="Thu, 24 Oct 2013 13:27:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch overloads all IOUtils buffer and toBuffered* methods with a size parameter to specify the desired buffer size.  I felt this was a more flexible solution than the original request of using a system wide property.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13804807" author="belugabehr" created="Thu, 24 Oct 2013 23:31:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Awesome.  Thanks for implementing it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
